## Dark Mode Fixes (Invoice Modal)
Added missing Tailwind `dark:` modifiers to the Invoice Detail pane to ensure readability against the dark theme background. 
* Applied `dark:text-slate-200`/`400` to labels and values.
* Applied `dark:bg-slate-800/80` and complementary border colors to the summary cards and table separators.

